                     <interp inst="t18261026-124-off681" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18261026-124-cd682" type="crimeDate">7th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18261026-124-off681 t18261026-124-cd682"></join>, 1 miniature-painting, value 5s.; 1 shirt, value 1s. 6d.; 3 handkerchiefs, value 6s. 6d.; 1 cap, value 3s. 6d.; 1 pin, value 3s., and 1 pair of scissors, value 6d.
            </rs>, the goods of 
